Detailed Description

template<class V>
class DWFCore::DWFWCharKeyChainedSkipList< V >

A chained skip list collection template that uses const wchar_t* string keys.

Since:
1.0.1
Note:
Key strings are not copied into the list and therefore must not be destroyed while the key is in use by the list.
Parameters:
V The value type.
